metadata.name: Proof of Steak #1/50
metadata.description:
At first, I created this room to participate in a fun game. Today, I want to share it to express my gratitude to the team and the community.

All funds will be used to reinvest in the poser collection and purchase new poser. When 50 pieces of Proof of Steak are sold, one of the Proof of Steak holders will receive a real poser.

/// Let's cook together! WE ARE POSERS!

[ ! please note I am a vegetarian xD ]
